{"tid":1690063,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"消防手足 你地真係忍得落？","createTime":"2019-11-03T06:37:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T08:00:10.000Z","uid":307389,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fc23f5930de9c5486c6aabad70413dca8b7f3625","tid":1690063,"uid":307389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:37:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">班人渣對住消防射<br />\n又爆粗又打鳩消防<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明顯係同我地過唔去<br />\n<br />\n救火雖然係搵命搏<br />\n但救火唔包俾槍射喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n現場嘅有眼睇<br />\n粒中國制催淚彈根本係燃燒彈<br />\n掉出嚟噴火噴成分鐘仲要炸傷左急救員<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n消防都係人<br />\n消防遇到恐怖分子都要自衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用消防喉驅散恐怖分子都好應該<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"8a8572ab6055e2ada54fbb32227393604127c4e1","tid":1690063,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:30:59.000Z","msg":"支持消防哥哥<br />\n<br />\nbtw發夢中後排可唔可以click入黎睇睇 thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出到黎可唔可以緊張少少 審時度勢..<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689923</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5c7202a624d6dbb2951a904da66809a0069b5e24","tid":1690063,"uid":316491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:00:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其實人同狗裝備差距好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但有消防出黃金戰衣<br />\n出埋雲梯細搶就完全唔同講法</span><br />\n<br />\n【突發】估唔到哨兵都認同呢樣嘢<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/esdQjS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/esdQjS</a>"}]}